[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating System.exit behavior**\n\nI’m thinking about why the main startAnt doesn’t catch after System.exit. It seems that System.exit can invoke a checkExit, throwing a SecurityException that propagates out. Since startAnt has System.exit after the try block, maybe that’s why it doesn’t catch. The catch for processArgs with System.exit(1) doesn't seem relevant here. Later, since System.exit(exitCode) appears after the finally block and isn’t enclosed, that exception can propagate to the test. It's good to clarify this!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0b6eeac6b52172910169efcb05655c819397bc1f005f9d7bc4\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp78sZR2IqV79UEjMzZ-uSgbRTVav45A3u973ctcx4GQajKS8dA7f_KUsEGNo4fRmD5fgmaQ_4NKeMP0JhsCrsEqmesazFIEWx7qQY7IcQmDqGCVqmqpHlumtHFgBSyE4Is4Py-tn1RTUbw7FWSmuwQJTWbPi3ES94J5hcxV90bJS8bqYOx8FreFQI1bRm17AinhRDhCE_nET0NfDphuD0DFi9zMXTh53HA20L1Ra5oQDAicWArswQzz5x1er2QJYYRKSJ6abEs6P6JspV-76e0WRWtr-o2vWq_NZPkkF3WmM1c9wpThf5pnqsbQ8mrcrDKQSQXY5CDScfl4FQ9Vp0vx1cNG2dxklMEaT9KPlE7KdG-JzZwLDsQS8nWVCenyc269REwXH287lnSpDraAQAF09zcRJVFbYvHiYaPCXjnFWathTH_oBChyBlku4rRU72csMcZxl-DrY1YHPns0bYRiQceDGGS0KMJMqPmvX-hVSRIc0arGTXH-joz1FR94wOI-Prx0lK0H1JayCw9GK7rQX3jrGJNQGBzsrAVyJ4aAZ89IosTzXUuYKPq_PxTxya4VGC6yBHg9asI2WL8dMZG1iA6IdflgSkhVTdLgDI1JSS6k8AMhhd-1MLeejpyOemWEWhrKRyT0bfHDrEuEX5mPNy0U3aMllSK1SOf8CV3Ngp74bjXUGwORiK8W4SCQCKfXl2BZo5Q3wMJdDui0XN3XV8qIaW3ACSiTXyHBbPI_V4MFd-ToGJU-brSKhv0LE9l7bDm0BjHn4kViZsfr72yl5CxyTZj0KiWMKUxi98tZzcCUYbRIx4jfY0H49OkxPxBBsL8JWIim4BCe6o_C1i0fV0pcdDSTRGaseg9HR0fKIXHkpkKejGPN5kFdyCdtQYwmWtQbM8U4-E8roMoJs5JB-4c37aA-FxgesOE5J8JoqIOpT1nQf8C0h_L05uGcvZOcU4_Aj8fMVg_SjpSsAnhzd2Gcwle_kK7dZmuKwYBo8EefhK7ZVlKC65sf7Q36QOUIpXAAKXBDyS_HAJWp3sNyj6QgajIUNx4t-ls2b7EQfTCqt3HtxK6OL-pT10vtYHwVRDmUCgXD3UzOBQHlZ60skVpuSciyQ_KoyKF9azjnc01uwyjvXxp1KXBcHErnV5v1c9m_76-cAEqgYVJgZMbQNLT7rQyliYPzLxJh3dV2Soq6J0s2UbIEyvYAsIl3pk_J